{"tid":1438313,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"拉實屋企老母唔好比佢去上環買海味 食到肚痛冇命賠","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:56:54.000Z","uid":232237,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6492d5df7d4cda9840021b69bc71f2a538c131e3","tid":1438313,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"呢到有單假人發現案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說老母星期三唔知死去上環買左海參番來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚發起左整 左海參炆雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家<em></em>食果陣已經覺得甘甘地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同平時陣味唔到宜家同<br />\n講 食完之後全家都肚痛係咁去廁所<br />\n都唔知係唔係比popo  毒煙污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母死口唔認 話人地落曬閘 又啤好左唔會有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔撚理 大家宜家屙 到菊花都裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撚知佢係唔係事後先啤番<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一於 有殺錯冇放過 建議巴絲睇實屋企老母 <br />\n唔好比佢地做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb3fb3deac53ab3e659e616c49a0a64b7de2cf6","tid":1438313,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屙完個肚仲係唔舒服 屌"},{"pid":"73bf6a97c10a724b637eaae626f59ff90d40671f","tid":1438313,"uid":11798,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:41:40.000Z","msg":"上環好多都大減價 <br />\n大家心照啦"},{"pid":"5bb6e09156d77b6afc72d4484beba25bf79e2ee7","tid":1438313,"uid":59501,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:43:49.000Z","msg":"分分鐘有毒<br />\n去醫院checkcheck穩陣"},{"pid":"cacb43a34d798cb303fcdb7d74e080cb2306c0c8","tid":1438313,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73bf6a97c10a724b637eaae6